                    <div class="feedback-quote">
                        <blockquote>
                            "SPIN's community welcomed me from day one. The networking opportunities are exceptional."
                        </blockquote>
                        <cite>- Dr. Yuki Nakamura, Recent Graduate</cite>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
